{"tid":1991313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實中聯辦有沒有根據社團條例註冊?","createTime":"2020-04-27T10:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T14:29:48.000Z","uid":36901,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f4752137869ee77826f81c8c4584b50a0815af","tid":1991313,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例第151章《社團條例》，所有在香港成立的組織都須於其成立一個月內註冊為社團，但已根據其他條例註冊的組織除外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦前身新華社有冇社團註冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果冇佢用乜註冊?新聞機構?<br />\n咁中聯辦唔通係傳媒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂喂喂，咁中聯辦個東主係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582d24aeb6d16797724d8971010f6b3756dc614c","tid":1991313,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1720b5eed8579f26bd5034d2f1591d1992023a4","tid":1991313,"uid":237425,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係22條即係唔屬中央政府？咁個d咩印花稅要交番齊wo 唔該"},{"pid":"42644f444b9c4d8750d33e7e35a8b89dc6497ab6","tid":1991313,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊條撚樣<br />\n快啲答<br />\n中聯辦係根據香港乜嘢條例而成立嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c48c62e3a0886bcb9e295b72d5ed23b7c2278c","tid":1991313,"uid":34681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:49:53.000Z","msg":"耐人尋味"},{"pid":"d19b00cf855b34a7d36a7c2a6639cf8f6f03ed9e","tid":1991313,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"開賓館做雞竇都要攞牌啦"},{"pid":"47f25e15257398ad50e72112763f37399da6b271","tid":1991313,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ad613ee7fd232067bed2772be